<B>Company Information:</B><BR>
RAVISENT's digital solutions incorporate industry standards for audio/video compression and internet access, independent of operating systems and silicon components.  They are built using a single, powerful, easily customizable and modular software architecture.  RAVISENT's products integrate this high-performance software tool kit and code base across multiple applicatons and multiple platforms.  This allows personal computer and consumer electronics manufacturers to achieve faster time-to-market, to cross-market their product offerings, to develop a customizable, consistent look and feel across product  lines, and to reduce technical support costs.  Our suite of modular software technology building blocks includes MPEG-2 real-time encoders and decoders; digital audio/video stream management components; Internet enabling technologies; integrated user interface applications; and a wide variety of supporting hardware reference designs.<BR>


